from user posts. Subsequently, it could be triggered everytime the user posts a new post or as and when triggered by the user. User could choose to use only tie-strength feature set (by providing only post as user input) or all features for learning and classiﬁcation.
User starts by choosing friends from a set of pre-deﬁned groups or selects everyone of his friends as the intended audience for the post. Service is invoked before posting this new information. The learnt model is then utilised to suggest friends who do not match the learnt model and need to be reviewed as possible unintended audience, by the user, before posting.

networks, thereby assisting user in maintaining consistent privacy across all social networks.

